\b \cf0 Introduction\

\b0 \
The Peer Review/Oversight System (PROS) comprises a software-based management system for creating, exchanging and responding to peer group performance questionnaires. Such questionnaires, or surveys, allow a group of peers to grade and review each other with respect to criteria (questions) proposed by the creator of the survey. Zero or more nominated overseer(s) may optionally review all exchanged evaluations by peers in each survey process.\
\
The system will comprise a web app, implemented in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES5), PHP and MySQL.\
